// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0237 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 5f5ae718-f455-5a30-a904-1be7f5da5890

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *amazonlinux:2* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:6* OR ImageFileName = *oraclelinux:7*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
